Senior Design Engineer ( Wellhead and Xmas Tree)
Senior Design Engineer ( Wellhead and Xmas Tree)
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  negotiableAmoria Bond is pleased to offer a unique opportunity within a well-reputed, multinational Oil & Gas company who require a Senior Engineer.
This role will be primarily based in Singapore on a permanent basis.
The successful candidate will have a career background focused on Surface or Subsea Equipment design and a good understanding of industry standards (API 6A). The ideal candidate will have more than 5 years of experience in engineering design and with Bachelors Degree or above in Mechanical Engineering or Petroleum/Oil/Gas Engineering. If you are motivated towards building up specialism in respect to wellhead design and manufacture then this opportunity is definitely something to seriously take a look at.
Salaries will be dependent on skill set and experience but will be competitive.
If you are available immediately and would like further information on this role please forward your CV for immediate consideration to charlotte . chicv @ amoriabond . com
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business. No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
